# Director of Product Design – Readiness Map

## Role scope (context)

- Set design vision and strategy; align design work to business and product objectives.
- Build and lead a high‑performing design team, including hiring, coaching, and performance management.
- Oversee end‑to‑end product design quality across multiple surfaces and initiatives.
- Implement and evolve design systems, research practices, and metrics that scale.

