## Prepare a portfolio of project work

**Goal:** Show business impact, systems thinking, and leadership—not just visuals.

What to include:
- 3–5 case studies with: context, constraints, your role, process, tradeoffs, and outcomes.
- Impact metrics: conversion, activation, retention, NPS, support volume, time to ship, etc.
- Systems work: design systems, workflows, research programs, experimentation, or process change.
- Leadership: how you set vision, aligned stakeholders, unblocked teams, mentored designers, and influenced the roadmap.

Examples and references:
- Example complex/identity portfolio:  
  - [Sarah B – IndyKite case study](https://www.sarahb-uxd.com/indykite)
